'''网络即服务'''（[[英语|英语]]：'''Network as a service''', '''NaaS'''）是一种用于网络传输连接的服务。<ref name="focus">{{cite web|title=ITU Focus Group on Cloud Computing - Part 1|url=http://www.itu.int/en/ITU-T/focusgroups/cloud/Documents/FG-coud-technical-report.zip|accessdate=2013-09-16|date=February 2012|publisher=International Telecommunication Union (ITU) Telecommunications Sector|archive-date=2016-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160616144015/http://www.itu.int/en/ITU-T/focusgroups/cloud/Documents/FG-coud-technical-report.zip|dead-url=no}}</ref>NaaS通过将网络和计算资源化作统一整体来进行资源分配的优化。<ref>{{cite web|title=Cloud computing in Telecommunications|url=http://www.ericsson.com/res/thecompany/docs/publications/ericsson_review/2010/cloudcomputing.pdf|accessdate=2012-12-16|publisher=Ericsson|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304093715/http://www.ericsson.com/res/thecompany/docs/publications/ericsson_review/2010/cloudcomputing.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 描述 ==
NaaS有时也包括由网络基础结构的所有者向第三方提供虚拟网络服务。<ref name="Eurescom">{{cite web|title=Network Virtualisation – Opportunities and Challenges|url=http://archive.eurescom.eu/~pub/deliverables/documents/P1900-series/P1956/D1/P1956-D1.pdf|accessdate=2012-12-16|date=2010-12-23|publisher={{tsl|en|Eurescom||Eurescom}}|archive-date=2013-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130406133542/http://archive.eurescom.eu/~pub/deliverables/documents/P1900-series/P1956/D1/P1956-D1.pdf|dead-url=no}}<!-- hangs for me? --></ref>通常，这将使用一些协议（如[[OpenFlow|OpenFlow]]等）进行网络虚拟化。<ref name="role">{{cite web|title=The role of virtualisation in future network architectures|url=http://www.change-project.eu/fileadmin/publications/Presentations/CHANGE_-_The_role_of_virtualisation_in_future_network_infrastructures_-_Warsaw_cluster_workshop_contribution.pdf|accessdate=2013-09-16|author=Ádám Kapovits|date=2011-06-14|publisher=Change Project|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304030914/http://www.change-project.eu/fileadmin/publications/Presentations/CHANGE_-_The_role_of_virtualisation_in_future_network_infrastructures_-_Warsaw_cluster_workshop_contribution.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

一些NaaS服务模式如：<ref name="focus" /><ref name="role" />

* [[虛擬私人網路|虚拟专用网络]]（VPN）：在诸如公共Internet的网络之间扩展专用网络以及网络中包含的资源。它能够让主机在共享或公用网络上发送和接收数据。<ref name="aryaka">{{cite web|title=Network as-a-Service: Consistent, optimized performance for the enterprise WAN without the high cost of MPLS|url=http://www.aryaka.com/products/network-as-a-service/|accessdate=2013-09-16|publisher=Aryaka Networks|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130807123708/http://www.aryaka.com/products/network-as-a-service/|archivedate=2013-08-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* 按需分配宽带（Bandwidth on Demand, BoD）：一种根据不同的节点或用户之间的要求来分配网络容量的技术。在此情况下，链路的速率可以动态地适应连接到链路节点的流量需求。<ref>{{cite web|title=Network as-a-Service|url=http://www.aryaka.com/products/network-as-a-service/|publisher=Aryaka Networks|access-date=2020-12-14|archive-date=2013-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130807123708/http://www.aryaka.com/products/network-as-a-service/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=NaaS: Network-as-a-Service in the Cloud|url=http://www.doc.ic.ac.uk/~costa/papers/costa12naas.pdf|accessdate=2012-12-16|last=Costa|first=Paulo|publisher=Imperial College London|author2=Migliavacca, Matteo|author3=Pietzuch, Peter|author4=Wolf, Alexander|archive-date=2012-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120617104050/http://www.doc.ic.ac.uk/~costa/papers/costa12naas.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* 移动网络虚拟化：电信或独立网络运营商构建和运营网络（无线或传输链路）并通过产能利用率向第三方（通常是移动电话运营商）出售其通信访问功能。<ref>{{cite web|title=Network virtualization Enabling novel business models in a dynamic market|url=http://www.nokiasiemensnetworks.com/sites/default/files/document/nsn-noo-2012_networkvirtualization_v01.pdf|accessdate=2012-12-16|publisher=Nokia Siemens Networks|archive-date=2012-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121124101743/http://www.nokiasiemensnetworks.com/sites/default/files/document/nsn-noo-2012_networkvirtualization_v01.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[移动虚拟运营商|移动虚拟运营商]]（MVNO）不拥有用来提供服务的无线电频谱或无线网络基础设施。通常MVNO使用已经建立的移动网络运营商的网络基础设施提供通信服务。<ref>{{cite web|title=Network Virtualization: Technologies, Perspectives, and Frontiers|url=http://www.nec-labs.com/~rajesh/nvs.html|accessdate=2012-12-17|last=Wang|first=Anjing|publisher=North Carolina State University|author2=Iyer, Mohan|author3=Dutta, Rudra|author4=Rouskas, George|author5=Baldine, Ilia|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304074741/http://www.nec-labs.com/~rajesh/nvs.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

